    <section>
      <h2 id="communication">Communications</h2>

      <h3>Internet Country Code</h3>

        <p>China's country code is .cn
        <br>The country's official web site can be found at:<a href="http://www.gov.cn/english/">www.GOV.cn</a></p>

      <h3>Internet Users</h3>

        <p>According to data, 54.3 percent of the Chinese population(751,886,119) has access to the internet by July.2018.</p>

      <h3>Broadband</h3>

        <p>407.382 million Chinese have subcription to broadband Internet, which means in 100 people there are 29 of them are subscribers.</p>

